A policewoman is among the two victims who survived with serious injuries in a crash involved a truck and other two vehicles on the N4 in KaNyamazane near Mbombela in Mpumalanga yesterday. Community safety, security and liaison provincial spokesperson Moeti Mmusi said one of the vehicles overturned and one occupant was declared dead on the spot. Moeti said the exact cause of the accident was under investigation. “One person died on the scene. The other two seriously injured include a female police officer. They were rushed to Nelspruit Medi-clinic in Mbombela,” Mmusi said. francen@thenewage.co.za